review: I have been consulting Doctor Latha Kanchi since my child was born and till date she is my only Doctor for my child Wellness checkups and all issues, My kid is three years old and we have crossed many issues like food allergies when he was three months old  , he suffered hives due to breast feeding where I had taken new kind of protein shake which caused him hives , constipation when introduced new formula arround two months old , then monthly vaccination till two years , Covid when he was seven months old , season flu,cold , dry cough issues , and child growth related checkups, everything Doctor gave him the right medication to overcome it faster and she gives the best guidance, Grateful and Thank You Doctor, She has become a Family Doctor I would say .
